# Security Checklist

- [ ] `DEV_AUTH_ENABLED` is set to `false` in production.
- [ ] `JWT_SECRET` and `SESSION_SECRET` are long, random strings.
- [ ] `PARENT_EMAILS` contain only authorized parent emails.
- [ ] Google OAuth Redirect URIs are correctly configured in Google Cloud Console.
- [ ] Cloudflare Tunnel hostname matches `PUBLIC_APP_URL` and `GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI`.
- [ ] `CORS_ORIGINS` is restricted to the production domain.
- [ ] SQLite database is backed up regularly.
- [ ] No secrets are committed to version control.
- [ ] Dependencies are kept up to date.
